text: Cooke County is a county in the U.S. state of Texas. In 2020, the population was estimated at 41,668. The county seat is Gainesville. == Geography == The county has a total area of 898 square miles. == Places == === Cities === * Callisburg * Gainesville (county seat) * Lindsay * Muenster * Valley View === Town === * Oak Ridge * Road Runner == References == Category:Texas counties
title: Cooke County, Texas
